headline: Penn State Extension cuts the ribbon on new Bucks County headquarters
author: Jeff Werner
sentences: On April 13, the Bucks County Commissioners joined extension leaders and the Penn State Nittany Lion in cutting the ribbon on its new headquarters at the Middletown Grange Fairgrounds in Wrightstown Township.
